splay, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn84020657, 1921-02-22, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ak", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "juneau (alaska)", "united states", "juneau", "alaska"], "subject_headings": ["Juneau (Alaska)--Newspapers", "Alaska--Juneau", "United States--Alaska--Juneau"], "subjects": [{"alaska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alaska&fo=json"}, {"juneau": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:juneau&fo=json"}, {"juneau (alaska)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:juneau+%28alaska%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T23:03:21.636Z", "title": "The Alaska daily empire (Juneau, Alaska), February 22, 1921", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020657/1921-02-22/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020657/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84020657"], "batch": ["ak_albatross_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1912", "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Vol. 1, no. 1 (Nov. 2, 1912)-v. 29, no. 4345 (Dec. 7, 1926). Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Daily Alaska empire 2771-2648 (D