 single maps and may also include some multi-sheet single maps, plates from atlases, books or periodicals, and printed facsimiles. These maps may also show various subjects, such as recreation and tourism. To request a specific map or for more information, contact a reference librarian in the Geography & Map Division (202) 707-6277 or through the \"Ask a librarian\" link through the Geography & Map Division website https://ask.loc.gov/map-geography/. Title supplied by cataloger. If a map in this collection may be in copyright, there is no online image available. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-04-29T15:17:56.090Z", "group": ["gmd/multimap", "catalog-split-07", "catalog", "multimaps", "main-catalog-split-07"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2022589353/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:50:ak-050:ak5027/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:50:ak-050:ak5027/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1636&w=5687", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:gmd:gmdtitlecolmaps:ak:-0:50:ak-050:ak5027/full/pct:25/0/default.jpg#h=3273&w=11375"], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["juneau", "klukwan", "alaska", "united states"], "mime_type": ["image/tiff", "image/jpeg", "image/jp2"], "number": ["2022589353", "2025-06-07t11:32:21.300000", "sheet", "2024-11-14t12:10:31"], "online_format": ["image"], "original_format": ["map", "collection"], "other_title": ["Alternate supplied title: Alaska title collection--drawer 50", "Alternate supplied title: Alaska title collection--cities and towns Juneau-Klukwan"], "partof": ["catalog", "geography and map division", "general maps", "cities and towns", "single sheet maps, title collection"], "score": 28.546068, "shelf_id": "G4374 coll .M3 drawer 50", "site": ["catalog"], "subject": ["tourist m